.TH MAKEBREAD 1 "February 2026" "makebread 0.4.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
makebread \- recipe manager for bread baking
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B makebread
[\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B makebread
is a GTK4/Adwaita recipe manager for bread baking. It provides a searchable
database of bread recipes with ingredients, instructions, and timers.
.PP
Features include recipe favorites, CSV/JSON export, Swedish translation support,
and keyboard shortcuts.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-version
Show version information and exit.
.TP
.B \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.SH KEYBOARD SHORTCUTS
.TP
.B Ctrl+Q
Quit the application.
.TP
.B Ctrl+E
Export recipes to CSV or JSON.
.TP
.B Ctrl+/
Show keyboard shortcuts.
.TP
.B F5
Refresh recipe list.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/makebread/settings.json
User settings and favorites.
